---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
import ButtonScrollTop from "../../components/buttons/ButtonScrollTop";
---
<link rel="canonical" href="https://cayadservices.com/data-deletion/" />
<style>
  .custom-background {
    background:
      linear-gradient(hsla(250, 75%, 5%, 0.5), rgba(6, 3, 21, 0.5)),
      url("/img/data.webp") center center no-repeat;
    background-size: cover;
  }
</style>

<Layout title="Data Deletion Instructions | Cayad Auto Transport"
content="Instructions to request deletion of your data from Cayad Auto Transport's WhatsApp Business API and services.">
  <container
    class="container-fluid flex flex-col items-center justify-center custom-background h-[60vh]"
  >
    <div class="w-[80%]">
      <h2
        class="text-white text-[4rem] xs:text-[1.8rem] sm:text-[1.8rem] font-bold"
        data-aos="fade-down"
      >
        Data Deletion Instructions
      </h2>
    </div>
  </container>

  <container
    class="w-[80%] xs:w-full xs:px-4 sm:w-full sm:px-4 flex flex-col mb-8 mx-auto"
  >
    <h1 class="text-3xl mt-8 font-semibold text-[#00000] w-full text-left">
      Request to Delete Your Data
    </h1>

    <p class="text-[#555] mt-8 text-left">
      At Cayad Services LLC ("Cayad", "we", "us", "our"), we respect your privacy and your right to control your personal data. This page provides instructions on how to request the deletion of your data that we have collected through our WhatsApp Business API integration and other services.
    </p>

    <div class="bg-blue-50 border-l-4 border-blue-500 p-4 mt-8 w-full text-left">
      <p class="text-blue-700 font-bold">Summary</p>
      <p class="text-blue-600 mt-2">To request deletion of your data, email <strong>info@cayadservices.com</strong> with the subject line "Data Deletion Request" from the email address associated with your account. Include your WhatsApp phone number with country code. We will process your request within 30 days.</p>
    </div>

    <h3 class="text-2xl mt-8 font-semibold text-[#00000] w-full text-left">What Data Do We Collect?</h3>
    <p class="text-[#555] mt-2 text-left">
      When you interact with our WhatsApp Business API service, we may collect and store:
    </p>
    <ul class="list-disc text-[#555] mt-2 pl-8 text-left">
      <li>Your WhatsApp phone number (including country code)</li>
      <li>Message history (content of messages sent and received)</li>
      <li>Conversation metadata (timestamps, delivery status, read receipts)</li>
      <li>Your name and profile information (if provided during conversation)</li>
      <li>Any files, images, or documents shared through WhatsApp</li>
      <li>Customer service interactions and support tickets</li>
    </ul>

    <h3 class="text-2xl mt-8 font-semibold text-[#00000] w-full text-left">How to Request Data Deletion</h3>
    
    <h4 class="text-xl mt-4 font-semibold text-[#00000] w-full text-left">Option 1: Email Request (Recommended)</h4>
    <p class="text-[#555] mt-2 text-left">
      Send an email to <strong>info@cayadservices.com</strong> with the following information:
    </p>
    <ol class="list-decimal text-[#555] mt-2 pl-8 text-left">
      <li><strong>Subject line:</strong> "Data Deletion Request - WhatsApp"</li>
      <li><strong>Your full name:</strong> As registered with our service</li>
      <li><strong>WhatsApp phone number:</strong> Include full international format (e.g., +1 XXX XXX XXXX)</li>
      <li><strong>Email address:</strong> Associated with your account (if any)</li>
      <li><strong>Date of first interaction:</strong> Approximate date you started using our WhatsApp service (optional but helpful)</li>
    </ol>

    <h4 class="text-xl mt-4 font-semibold text-[#00000] w-full text-left">Option 2: Phone Request</h4>
    <p class="text-[#555] mt-2 text-left">
      Call us at <strong>(469) 619-0747</strong> and ask to speak with our Data Privacy Officer. Please be prepared to verify your identity.
    </p>

    <h4 class="text-xl mt-4 font-semibold text-[#00000] w-full text-left">Option 3: WhatsApp Message</h4>
    <p class="text-[#555] mt-2 text-left">
      You may also send a message to our WhatsApp number requesting data deletion. Please include the word "DELETE" followed by your email address. We will follow up to verify your identity.
    </p>

    <h3 class="text-2xl mt-8 font-semibold text-[#00000] w-full text-left">Verification Process</h3>
    <p class="text-[#555] mt-2 text-left">
      To protect your privacy and prevent unauthorized deletions, we will verify your identity before processing any data deletion request. Verification may include:
    </p>
    <ul class="list-disc text-[#555] mt-2 pl-8 text-left">
      <li>Sending a confirmation code to your WhatsApp number</li>
      <li>Asking you to reply to a confirmation email</li>
      <li>Requesting additional identifying information</li>
    </ul>

    <h3 class="text-2xl mt-8 font-semibold text-[#00000] w-full text-left">Processing Timeline</h3>
    <p class="text-[#555] mt-2 text-left">
      Once we receive and verify your request:
    </p>
    <ul class="list-disc text-[#555] mt-2 pl-8 text-left">
      <li><strong>Acknowledgment:</strong> Within 48 business hours, we will confirm receipt of your request</li>
      <li><strong>Processing:</strong> We will complete the deletion within <strong>30 days</strong> of verification</li>
      <li><strong>Confirmation:</strong> You will receive a final confirmation email once deletion is complete</li>
    </ul>

    <h3 class="text-2xl mt-8 font-semibold text-[#00000] w-full text-left">What Gets Deleted</h3>
    <p class="text-[#555] mt-2 text-left">
      Upon successful verification, we will delete:
    </p>
    <ul class="list-disc text-[#555] mt-2 pl-8 text-left">
      <li>All message history and conversation logs</li>
      <li>Your WhatsApp phone number from our active databases</li>
      <li>Any personal information collected during conversations</li>
      <li>Uploaded files, images, or documents shared via WhatsApp</li>
      <li>Customer service interaction records</li>
    </ul>

    <h3 class="text-2xl mt-8 font-semibold text-[#00000] w-full text-left">What We May Retain</h3>
    <p class="text-[#555] mt-2 text-left">
      In certain circumstances, we may need to retain some data even after a deletion request:
    </p>
    <ul class="list-disc text-[#555] mt-2 pl-8 text-left">
      <li><strong>Legal obligations:</strong> Data required by law, regulation, or legal process</li>
      <li><strong>Fraud prevention:</strong> Information needed to prevent or investigate fraud</li>
      <li><strong>Security:</strong> Data necessary to maintain security of our systems</li>
      <li><strong>Backup systems:</strong> Residual data in backup systems (retained for up to 90 days, then automatically deleted)</li>
    </ul>

    <h3 class="text-2xl mt-8 font-semibold text-[#00000] w-full text-left">California Residents (CCPA/CPRA)</h3>
    <p class="text-[#555] mt-2 text-left">
      If you are a California resident, you have the right to:
    </p>
    <ul class="list-disc text-[#555] mt-2 pl-8 text-left">
      <li>Request deletion of your personal data</li>
      <li>Know what personal data we collect about you</li>
      <li>Opt-out of the sale or sharing of your personal data (we do not sell your data)</li>
      <li>Not be discriminated against for exercising your rights</li>
    </ul>
    <p class="text-[#555] mt-4 text-left">
      To exercise your California privacy rights, please email <strong>info@cayadservices.com</strong> with "California Privacy Request" in the subject line.
    </p>

    <h3 class="text-2xl mt-8 font-semibold text-[#00000] w-full text-left">EU Residents (GDPR)</h3>
    <p class="text-[#555] mt-2 text-left">
      If you are a resident of the European Economic Area (EEA), you have the following rights under GDPR:
    </p>
    <ul class="list-disc text-[#555] mt-2 pl-8 text-left">
      <li><strong>Right to erasure (Article 17):</strong> Request deletion of your personal data</li>
      <li><strong>Right to access (Article 15):</strong> Request a copy of your data</li>
      <li><strong>Right to rectification (Article 16):</strong> Correct inaccurate data</li>
      <li><strong>Right to restrict processing (Article 18):</strong> Limit how we use your data</li>
      <li><strong>Right to data portability (Article 20):</strong> Receive your data in a machine-readable format</li>
      <li><strong>Right to object (Article 21):</strong> Object to certain types of processing</li>
    </ul>
    <p class="text-[#555] mt-4 text-left">
      To exercise your GDPR rights, email <strong>info@cayadservices.com</strong>. You also have the right to lodge a complaint with your local supervisory authority.
    </p>

    <h3 class="text-2xl mt-8 font-semibold text-[#00000] w-full text-left">Sample Email Template</h3>
    <div class="bg-gray-100 p-6 mt-4 rounded-lg w-full text-left">
      <p class="font-mono text-sm whitespace-pre-wrap">
<strong>To:</strong> info@cayadservices.com<br/>
<strong>Subject:</strong> Data Deletion Request - WhatsApp<br/>
<br/>
Dear Cayad Privacy Team,<br/>
<br/>
I am requesting the deletion of all personal data you have collected from me through your WhatsApp Business API service.<br/>
<br/>
<strong>My information:</strong><br/>
- Full name: [Your full name]<br/>
- WhatsApp number: [Your number with country code, e.g., +1 XXX XXX XXXX]<br/>
- Email associated with account: [Your email address]<br/>
<br/>
Please confirm receipt of this request and notify me once deletion is complete.<br/>
<br/>
Thank you,<br/>
[Your name]
      </p>
    </div>

    <h3 class="text-2xl mt-8 font-semibold text-[#00000] w-full text-left">Contact Information</h3>
    <p class="text-[#555] mt-2 text-left">
      For questions about data deletion or privacy concerns:
    </p>
    <p class="text-[#555] mt-4 text-left">
      <strong>Cayad Services LLC</strong><br />
      Attn: Data Privacy Officer<br />
      7901 4th St N<br />
      St. Petersburg, FL 33702<br />
      <strong>Email:</strong> info@cayadservices.com<br />
      <strong>Phone:</strong> (469) 619-0747
    </p>

    <div class="bg-yellow-50 border-l-4 border-yellow-500 p-4 mt-8 w-full text-left">
      <p class="text-yellow-700 font-bold">Important Notes</p>
      <p class="text-yellow-600 mt-2">
        • Deletion requests are free of charge<br/>
        • We will never charge a fee to delete your data<br/>
        • You will not be penalized for requesting deletion<br/>
        • Some services may be impacted if data required for service delivery is deleted<br/>
        • Keep your confirmation email as proof of your request.
      </p>
    </div>

    
  </container>

  <ButtonScrollTop client:load />
</Layout>